title: Age.of.Empires.Definitive.Edition-CODEX
description:
C O D E X
P R E S E N T S

Age of Empires: Definitive Edition (c) Microsoft

Release Date :  02/2018              Protection : Microsoft+Arxan
Discs        :  1                    Genre      : Strategy

Age of Empires, the  pivotal RTS  that launched  a  20-year  legacy
returns in definitive form for Windows 10  PCs.  Bringing  together
all of the officially released content  with  modernized  gameplay,
all-new visuals and a host of other new features, Age  of  Empires:
Definitive Edition is the complete RTS package. Engage in  over  40
hours of updated campaign content with new  narration  and  pacing,
jump online in up to 8-player battles with new competitive features
and modes, experience 4K HD visuals with overhauled animations, get
creative  with  the  scenario  builder and  share  your  creations.
There  s never been a better time  to jump  in to  Age  of  Empires.
Welcome back to history.

- Extract
- Burn or mount the .iso
- Run SetAoEDE.exe and install
- Let our installer copy the crack for you!
- Play from Start Menu Shortcut!!

Notes:

This game requires Windows 10 version 1607 or newer to play.
The first patch is included (v1.3.5101.2/Build 5101).

Included languages:

en-us, es-es, es-mx, pt-br, de-de, fr-fr, hi-in, it-it, ja-jp, ko-kr,
ru-ru, vi-vn, zh-cn, zh-tw

General Notes:

- Block the game's exe in your firewall to prevent the game from
trying to go online ..

nothing but competition!
